descript.abstract: This data set is known as Flora Tree Species Site and locations and information about trees that may or may not be owned and maintained by the City of Bakersfield, CA.
descript.purpose: The data set was created to aid in local GIS and mapping applications and to allow the visualizations of city growth over the years.
